-- Banca Carige Is `Looking' at Banca Monte, Executive Tells la Repubblica
-- Sonia Sirletti
-- 2010-06-14T06:40:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/banca-carige-is-looking-at-banca-monte-executive-tells-la-repubblica.html

          
          
             Banca Carige SpA , an Italian
regional lender, is “looking” at Banca Monte Parma to expand
its business,  Repubblica  reported, citing an interview with
General Manager  Ennio La Monica .  
 Banca Monte Parma is seeking investors after the Bank of
Italy said it needed to increase capital, according to the
newspaper.  
